    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/841d04c7e97f2899d105699a4f7c9d6a.poster.avif?t=1770761127\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/841d04c7e97f2899d105699a4f7c9d6a.webm?t=1770761127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/841d04c7e97f2899d105699a4f7c9d6a.mp4?t=1770761127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/0a6ffd64ed62d6e1065b25775196e02b.poster.avif?t=1770761127\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/0a6ffd64ed62d6e1065b25775196e02b.webm?t=1770761127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/0a6ffd64ed62d6e1065b25775196e02b.mp4?t=1770761127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 关于本游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Momogatari 是一款专注于<strong>战斗表现力、即时适应能力与操作掌控感</strong>的 <strong>2D 动作银河恶魔城游戏</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演年轻的战士 <strong>桃太郎（Momotaro）</strong>，踏入名为 <strong>Yomi</strong> 的黑暗世界——这里充满了灵体、妖怪（Yokai）以及源自日本民间传说的强大神明（Kami）。<br>你所持有的神圣武器能够<strong>即时切换不同的剑型</strong>，在战斗中不断调整战术，对抗凶猛的敌人，并逐步揭开威胁至亲之人的诅咒真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的每一次遭遇都旨在考验你的<strong>决策能力</strong>，而不仅仅是反应速度。<br>观察敌人、预判行动，并在关键时刻选择合适的武器，是生存的关键。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ 主要特色</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >即时切换剑型的战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多种剑型之间自由切换，每种剑型都拥有独特的战斗机制与定位。<br>根据敌人的行为、站位与战斗压力，实时调整你的战斗策略。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精准而流畅的平台动作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动与战斗紧密结合。<br>跳跃、冲刺与站位需要精准执行，才能保持流畅的节奏与操作手感。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满挑战的敌人与 Boss 战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对精心设计的敌人和高强度的 Boss 战斗，<br>每一场战斗都围绕<strong>独特机制</strong>展开，鼓励学习与掌握，而非单纯的反复尝试。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >富有深度的成长系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过技能树塑造你的专属玩法。<br>技能升级将影响战斗方式、机动能力以及特殊技能，强调有意义的选择而非单纯数值提升。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的挑战内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>群敌挑战</strong>：考验你的空间意识与控场能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>式神（Shikigami）</strong>：召唤灵体盟友，拓展战斗与探索策略</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>节奏鼓挑战</strong>：以节奏与时机为核心的试炼玩法</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >灵感源自日本神话的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个相互连通、充满神话与传说的世界，<br>配合<strong>自适应音乐系统</strong>与传统日本乐器，营造沉浸式氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/d7dc2ad612d7fb3848d09289e42a4db5.poster.avif?t=1770761127\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/d7dc2ad612d7fb3848d09289e42a4db5.webm?t=1770761127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124660/extras/d7dc2ad612d7fb3848d09289e42a4db5.mp4?t=1770761127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
